LIB9(3)

NAME
	lib9 - Plan 9 compatibility library for TaijiOS

DESCRIPTION
	lib9 provides Plan 9 C library functions for TaijiOS, adapted
	from Inferno OS. It enables programs using Plan 9 conventions
	to compile and run on modern systems.

FUNCTIONS

	String formatting
		print, fprint, sprint, snprint, seprint, smprint
		fmtinstall, dostfmt, dorfmt

	Utility functions
		cleanname, argv0, exits, sysfatal
		tokenize, getfields, strdup, strecpy

	Unicode support
		utflen, utfnlen, utfrrune, utfrune, utfecpy
		runestrchr, runestrlen, runetype
		runeseprint, runesmprint, runesnprint

	9P protocol
		convD2M, convM2D, convM2S, convS2M
		fcallfmt

	Directory operations
		dirstat, dirwstat, create

SOURCE
	Adapted from Inferno OS lib9:
	https://github.com/inferno-os/inferno-os

BUILD

	mk		build liblib9.a
	mk install	install to $ROOT/lib
	mk clean	clean build artifacts

CONFIGURATION

	The mkfile selects platform-specific implementations:
	POSIX (Linux, BSD, macOS)
		errstr-posix, getuser-posix, getwd-posix

NOTES

	This library is maintained as part of TaijiOS. The original
	Inferno version targets multiple operating systems; this version
	is configured for POSIX systems only.

SEE ALSO
	marrow(8), kryon-wm(1), plan9port(1)
